gov.nih.nlm.mrd.common
Class QAComparisonReason

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.mrd.common.QAReason.Default
      gov.nih.nlm.mrd.common.QAComparisonReason
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, QAReason
public class QAComparisonReason
extends QAReason.Default

Represents a reason for a QAComparison discrepancy between two QA reports. This reason is used in a QAReport where there are differences between the counts of a matching name/value in two sets of QAResults.

Author:
TTN
